        <abstract>
            <p>Hybrid insects.</p>
            <p>Description of the Salvages.</p>
            <p>Variability of "transition groups" of insects; relation of variability to ranges of insects. The variability of wings, even within species. Reduction of flying ability on isolated islands.</p>
            <p>Forbes’s "Atlantis" theory and insect fauna of the Atlantic islands, considered with regard to insect migrations.</p>
        </abstract>
